window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jayne Frost and husband Sinclair Crowe are off on another adventure, this time to Nashville, a.k.a. Music City, to pay a royal visit to one of the Santa’s Workshops toy stores. Once that’s done, they’ll have a little time to sightsee and play tourist.<br> <br> Which they do. Until something rather peculiar happens in the Country Music Hall of Fame that leaves Sinclair feeling all shook up.<br> <br> Suddenly, they have a new mystery to solve. And time is ticking for Sinclair. Even a necromancer can only take so much.<br> <br> Can Jayne and Sinclair get to the bottom of things before it’s too late?</p>"; 
